33:10.689 --> 33:18.689
The Danish national
late night dish.

33:19.731 --> 33:21.766
John's hot dog?

33:21.767 --> 33:22.000
Yes.

33:22.001 --> 33:27.805
I'll have the deluxe.

33:27.806 --> 33:28.640
Organic sausage.

33:28.640 --> 33:29.608
Sounds good to me.

33:29.609 --> 33:32.977
He made his own mustard.

33:32.978 --> 33:34.045
Wow.

33:34.046 --> 33:34.280
Whoa.

